item.text: 30k USSR postage stamp depicting Sputnik 1 = [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sputnik_1#/media/File:1967_CPA_3496.jpg wikipedia]

Sputnik (meaning Elementary Satellite in Russian), was the first artificial Earth satellite. It was a 58 cm diameter polished metal sphere, with four external radio antennas to broadcast radio pulses - [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sputnik_1 wikipedia]
